stringStats.value: Bring this to the Ghost of Galaeral to gain access to the Lady Aerfalle, who presently resides in her deepest Sanctum.  **Be Warned: Only those of great skill (Level 150+) may enter the deepest sanctums and challenge Lady Aerfalle directly.  Also, you will need to be in a Fellowship to gain access to the Sanctum.
A shard of pure mana, attuned to the Nexus that lies deep under Aerlinthe Isle.  With the proper power, this could likely be used to create a portal to the nexus it is tied to.
